Signed-off-by: Gerd Hoffmann <kraxel@redhat.com>
Tested-by: Bruno Wolff III <bruno@wolff.to>
Cc: drm-intel-fixes@lists.freedesktop.org
Signed-off-by: Jani Nikula <jani.nikula@intel.com>
